content.p: To register, student must self-enroll via Moodle https://moodle.nottingham.ac.uk/course/view.php?id=141366 starting 09:00 (GMT + 8) on Tuesday, 1 October 2024, 10:00 AM Classes are scheduled to begin in November 2024.
